Package ui.base

Class DockedPageView

  • java.lang.Object
    • ui.base.DockedPageView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable, JPanelCardSlotContainer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InventoryFrame, ManagerManageEmployees, ManagerMenuCustomization, ManagersReportPage, MenuOrderScreen
    public abstract class DockedPageView
extends java.lang.Object
implements JPanelCardSlotContainer
    An abstract class representing a docked page view. This class provides a container for a JPanel-based workspace screen and manages the layout and navigation controllers.
